In [26]:
def walktree(top):
    values = top.groups.values()
    yield values
    for value in top.groups.values():
        for children in walktree(value):
            yield children

groupList=[]
for children in walktree(rootgrp):
    for child in children:
        print(child.name)
        groupList.append(child.name)

print(groupList)
